snippet.title: Johnny M In The Mix ►Dj Activities
snippet.description:
Hello, i'm Johnny M and i'm from Athens/Greece.
Playing and mixing music from 1999...
My favorite genres ofcourse are Greek music and especially Dance Hits but also i like mixing Deep, Tech, Progressive House, Trance, Chillout/Lounge and some times Rock, Disco from 80s & 90s
Thanks for visiting my page... enjoy my sets!!

Follow me...
